#. <section class="sutta" id="mn149"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn149:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 149"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 149"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn149:0.2"
msgid "Mahāsaḷāyatanikasutta"
msgstr "The Great Discourse on the Six Sense Fields"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn149:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "mn149:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "mn149:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "mn149:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "mn149:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:2.1"
msgid "“mahāsaḷāyatanikaṃ vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I shall teach you the great discourse on the six sense fields."

msgctxt "mn149:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "mn149:2.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "mn149:2.4"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, rūpe ajānaṃ apassaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, cakkhusamphassaṃ "
"ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, yamidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi ajānaṃ apassaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ, cakkhusmiṃ sārajjati, rūpesu sārajjati, cakkhuviññāṇe "
"sārajjati, cakkhusamphasse sārajjati, yamidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā "
"uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi "
"sārajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when you don’t truly know and see the eye, sights, eye "
"consciousness, eye contact, and what is felt as pleasant, painful, or "
"neutral that arises conditioned by eye contact, you’re aroused by desire for "
"these things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.288"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa sārattassa saṃyuttassa sammūḷhassa assādānupassino viharato āyatiṃ "
"pañcupādānakkhandhā upacayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who lives aroused like this—fettered, confused, concentrating on "
"gratification—accumulates the five grasping aggregates for themselves in the "
"future."

msgctxt "mn149:3.3"
msgid ""
"Taṇhā cassa ponobbhavikā nandīrāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, sā cassa "
"pavaḍḍhati."
msgstr ""
"And their craving—which leads to future rebirth, mixed up with relishing and "
"greed, looking for enjoyment in various different realms—grows."

msgctxt "mn149:3.4"
msgid "Tassa kāyikāpi darathā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi darathā pavaḍḍhanti;"
msgstr "Their physical and mental stress,"

msgctxt "mn149:3.5"
msgid "kāyikāpi santāpā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi santāpā pavaḍḍhanti;"
msgstr "torment,"

msgctxt "mn149:3.6"
msgid "kāyikāpi pariḷāhā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi pariḷāhā pavaḍḍhanti."
msgstr "and fever grow."

#. VAR: kāyadukkhampi → kāyika­duk­khampi (s1-3, km) | kāyikaṃ dukkhampi (mr)
msgctxt "mn149:3.7"
msgid "So kāyadukkhampi cetodukkhampi paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr "And they experience physical and mental suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4-7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:4-7.1"
msgid "Sotaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "When you don’t truly know and see the ear …"

msgctxt "mn149:4-7.2"
msgid "ghānaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "mn149:4-7.3"
msgid "jivhaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "mn149:4-7.4"
msgid "kāyaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "mn149:4-7.5"
msgid ""
"manaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, dhamme, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ "
"apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, manoviññāṇaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, "
"manosamphassaṃ, bhikkhave, ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, yamidaṃ "
"manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi ajānaṃ apassaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, manasmiṃ sārajjati, "
"dhammesu sārajjati, manoviññāṇe sārajjati, manosamphasse sārajjati, yamidaṃ "
"manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā "
"adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi sārajjati."
msgstr ""
"mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, mind contact, and what is felt as "
"pleasant, painful, or neutral that arises conditioned by mind contact, you’"
"re aroused by desire for these things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:8.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa sārattassa saṃyuttassa sammūḷhassa assādānupassino viharato āyatiṃ "
"pañcupādānakkhandhā upacayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who lives aroused like this—fettered, confused, concentrating on "
"gratification—accumulates the five grasping aggregates for themselves in the "
"future."

msgctxt "mn149:8.2"
msgid ""
"Taṇhā cassa ponobbhavikā nandīrāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, sā cassa "
"pavaḍḍhati."
msgstr ""
"And their craving—which leads to future rebirth, mixed up with relishing and "
"greed, looking for enjoyment in various different realms—grows."

msgctxt "mn149:8.3"
msgid "Tassa kāyikāpi darathā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi darathā pavaḍḍhanti;"
msgstr "Their physical and mental stress,"

msgctxt "mn149:8.4"
msgid "kāyikāpi santāpā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi santāpā pavaḍḍhanti;"
msgstr "torment,"

msgctxt "mn149:8.5"
msgid "kāyikāpi pariḷāhā pavaḍḍhanti, cetasikāpi pariḷāhā pavaḍḍhanti."
msgstr "and fever grow."

msgctxt "mn149:8.6"
msgid "So kāyadukkhampi cetodukkhampi paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr "And they experience physical and mental suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:9.1"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuñca kho, bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, rūpe jānaṃ passaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, cakkhusamphassaṃ jānaṃ "
"passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, yamidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ "
"sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, "
"cakkhusmiṃ na sārajjati, rūpesu na sārajjati, cakkhuviññāṇe na sārajjati, "
"cakkhusamphasse na sārajjati, yamidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi na sārajjati."
msgstr ""
"When you do truly know and see the eye, sights, eye consciousness, eye "
"contact, and what is felt as pleasant, painful, or neutral that arises "
"conditioned by eye contact, you’re not aroused by desire for these things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.289"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:9.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa asārattassa asaṃyuttassa asammūḷhassa ādīnavānupassino viharato āyatiṃ "
"pañcupādānakkhandhā apacayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who lives unaroused like this—unfettered, unconfused, concentrating "
"on drawbacks—disperses the the five grasping aggregates for themselves in "
"the future ."

msgctxt "mn149:9.3"
msgid ""
"Taṇhā cassa ponobbhavikā nandīrāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, sā cassa "
"pahīyati."
msgstr ""
"And their craving—which leads to future rebirth, mixed up with relishing and "
"greed, looking for enjoyment in various different realms—is given up."

msgctxt "mn149:9.4"
msgid "Tassa kāyikāpi darathā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi darathā pahīyanti;"
msgstr "Their physical and mental stress,"

msgctxt "mn149:9.5"
msgid "kāyikāpi santāpā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi santāpā pahīyanti;"
msgstr "torment,"

msgctxt "mn149:9.6"
msgid "kāyikāpi pariḷāhā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi pariḷāhā pahīyanti."
msgstr "and fever are given up."

msgctxt "mn149:9.7"
msgid "So kāyasukhampi cetosukhampi paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr "And they experience physical and mental pleasure."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:10.1"
msgid "Yā tathābhūtassa diṭṭhi sāssa hoti sammādiṭṭhi;"
msgstr "The view of such a person is right view."

msgctxt "mn149:10.2"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa saṅkappo svāssa hoti sammāsaṅkappo;"
msgstr "Their intention is right intention,"

msgctxt "mn149:10.3"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa vāyāmo svāssa hoti sammāvāyāmo;"
msgstr "their effort is right effort,"

msgctxt "mn149:10.4"
msgid "yā tathābhūtassa sati sāssa hoti sammāsati;"
msgstr "their mindfulness is right mindfulness,"

msgctxt "mn149:10.5"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa samādhi svāssa hoti sammāsamādhi."
msgstr "and their immersion is right immersion."

msgctxt "mn149:10.6"
msgid "Pubbeva kho panassa kāyakammaṃ vacīkammaṃ ājīvo suparisuddho hoti."
msgstr ""
"But their actions of body and speech have already been fully purified before."

msgctxt "mn149:10.7"
msgid "Evamassāyaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "So this noble eightfold path is developed to perfection."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:10.8"
msgid ""
"Tassa evaṃ imaṃ ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayato cattāropi satipaṭṭhānā "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, cattāropi sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, cattāropi iddhipādā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi indriyāni "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi balāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, "
"sattapi bojjhaṅgā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"When the noble eightfold path is developed, the following are developed to "
"perfection: the four kinds of mindfulness meditation, the four right "
"efforts, the four bases of psychic power, the five faculties, the five "
"powers, and the seven awakening factors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
#. VAR: yuganandhā → yuganaddhā (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn149:10.9"
msgid "Tassime dve dhammā yuganandhā vattanti—"
msgstr "And these two qualities proceed in conjunction:"

msgctxt "mn149:10.10"
msgid "samatho ca vipassanā ca."
msgstr "serenity and discernment."

msgctxt "mn149:10.11"
msgid "So ye dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā te dhamme abhiññā parijānāti."
msgstr ""
"They completely understand by direct knowledge those things that should be "
"completely understood by direct knowledge."

msgctxt "mn149:10.12"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā te dhamme abhiññā pajahati."
msgstr ""
"They give up by direct knowledge those things that should be given up by "
"direct knowledge."

msgctxt "mn149:10.13"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā te dhamme abhiññā bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"They develop by direct knowledge those things that should be developed by "
"direct knowledge."

msgctxt "mn149:10.14"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā te dhamme abhiññā sacchikaroti."
msgstr ""
"They realize by direct knowledge those things that should be realized by "
"direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:11.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā?"
msgstr ""
"And what are the things that should be completely understood by direct "
"knowledge?"

msgctxt "mn149:11.2"
msgid "‘Pañcupādānakkhandhā’ tissa vacanīyaṃ,"
msgstr "You should say: ‘The five grasping aggregates.’"

msgctxt "mn149:11.3"
msgid ""
"seyyathidaṃ—rūpupādānakkhandho, vedanupādānakkhandho, saññupādānakkhandho, "
"saṅkhārupādānakkhandho, viññāṇupādānakkhandho."
msgstr "That is: form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness."

msgctxt "mn149:11.4"
msgid "Ime dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā."
msgstr ""
"These are the things that should be completely understood by direct "
"knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:11.5"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be given up by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "mn149:11.6"
msgid "Avijjā ca bhavataṇhā ca—"
msgstr "Ignorance and craving for continued existence."

msgctxt "mn149:11.7"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā."
msgstr "These are the things that should be given up by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:11.8"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be developed by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "mn149:11.9"
msgid "Samatho ca vipassanā ca—"
msgstr "Serenity and discernment."

msgctxt "mn149:11.10"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr "These are the things that should be developed by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.290"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:11.11"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā?"
msgstr "And what are the things that should be realized by direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "mn149:11.12"
msgid "Vijjā ca vimutti ca—"
msgstr "Knowledge and freedom."

msgctxt "mn149:11.13"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā."
msgstr "These are the things that should be realized by direct knowledge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12-18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:12-18.1"
msgid "Sotaṃ, bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "When you truly know and see the ear …"

msgctxt "mn149:12-18.2"
msgid "ghānaṃ bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "mn149:12-18.3"
msgid "jivhaṃ, bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "mn149:12-18.4"
msgid "kāyaṃ, bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "mn149:12-18.5"
msgid ""
"manaṃ, bhikkhave, jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, dhamme jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, "
"manoviññāṇaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, manosamphassaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ "
"yathābhūtaṃ, yamidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi jānaṃ passaṃ yathābhūtaṃ, manasmiṃ na "
"sārajjati, dhammesu na sārajjati, manoviññāṇe na sārajjati, manosamphasse na "
"sārajjati, yamidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tasmimpi na sārajjati."
msgstr ""
"mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, mind contact, and what is felt as "
"pleasant, painful, or neutral that arises conditioned by mind contact, you "
"are not aroused by desire for these things. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:19.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa asārattassa asaṃyuttassa asammūḷhassa ādīnavānupassino viharato āyatiṃ "
"pañcupādānakkhandhā apacayaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:19.2"
msgid ""
"Taṇhā cassa ponobbhavikā nandīrāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, sā cassa "
"pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:19.3"
msgid "Tassa kāyikāpi darathā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi darathā pahīyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:19.4"
msgid "kāyikāpi santāpā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi santāpā pahīyanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:19.5"
msgid "kāyikāpi pariḷāhā pahīyanti, cetasikāpi pariḷāhā pahīyanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:19.6"
msgid "So kāyasukhampi cetosukhampi paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:20.1"
msgid "Yā tathābhūtassa diṭṭhi sāssa hoti sammādiṭṭhi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.2"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa saṅkappo svāssa hoti sammāsaṅkappo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.3"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa vāyāmo svāssa hoti sammāvāyāmo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.4"
msgid "yā tathābhūtassa sati sāssa hoti sammāsati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.5"
msgid "yo tathābhūtassa samādhi svāssa hoti sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.6"
msgid "Pubbeva kho panassa kāyakammaṃ vacīkammaṃ ājīvo suparisuddho hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:20.7"
msgid "Evamassāyaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:21.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa evaṃ imaṃ ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvayato cattāropi satipaṭṭhānā "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, cattāropi sammappadhānā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ "
"gacchanti, cattāropi iddhipādā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi indriyāni "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, pañcapi balāni bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti, "
"sattapi bojjhaṅgā bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:22.1"
msgid "Tassime dve dhammā yuganandhā vattanti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:22.2"
msgid "samatho ca vipassanā ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:22.3"
msgid "So ye dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā te dhamme abhiññā parijānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:22.4"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā te dhamme abhiññā pajahati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:22.5"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā te dhamme abhiññā bhāveti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:22.6"
msgid "Ye dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā te dhamme abhiññā sacchikaroti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya23"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:23.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:23.2"
msgid "‘Pañcupādānakkhandhā’ tissa vacanīyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:23.3"
msgid ""
"rūpupādānakkhandho, vedanupādānakkhandho, saññupādānakkhandho, "
"saṅkhārupādānakkhandho, viññāṇupādānakkhandho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:23.4"
msgid "Ime dhammā abhiññā pariññeyyā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya24"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:24.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:24.2"
msgid "Avijjā ca bhavataṇhā ca—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:24.3"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā pahātabbā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:25.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:25.2"
msgid "Samatho ca vipassanā ca—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:25.3"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā bhāvetabbā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:26.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:26.2"
msgid "Vijjā ca vimutti ca—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn149:26.3"
msgid "ime dhammā abhiññā sacchikātabbā”ti."
msgstr "These are the things that should be realized by direct knowledge.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn149:26.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn149:26.5"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn149:26.6"
msgid "Mahāsaḷāyatanikasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
